y recovers their HP, and fills<br>the skill gauge for Brilliant Bolt by 100%.<br>The second time this skill is used, a variant<br>with different effects will be used instead.<br>The skill will then alternate between these<br>two versions with every use. This skill will<br>not reset the user\'s energy level.<\/div><div class=\\"skill-detail\\">Skill Energy Required: 5,610<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbStrength +20%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u30fbHP Regen<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Potency: 10<br><br><color=#00008B>After Skill Change:<\/color><br>Skill Energy Required: 5,610<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbStrength +20%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u30fbDefense +20%<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u30fbHP Regen<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 15 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Potency: 10<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/b2f1d14494e80343f38734ca9a2b72842.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>Skill Haste +15%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIncreases skill gauge fill rate by 15%.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/3a59dbd2051c2865bdfc9245c709a80a2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Flame) Combo = Energy Level Up VI<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Flame: <br>increases their energy level by one stage<br>for every 20-hit combo.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/7ea00c46aa6b565d6054e18deab891fa2.png\\"><\/span><span>Sylvan Strength III<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases Sarisse\'s strength by 2% <br>and critical rate by 1% for 15 seconds<br>for every 20-hit combo.<br><br>Also, using Cheerful Assist will grant Sarisse<br>a strength amp with a maximum team amp level<br>of three and a defense amp with a maximum<br>team amp level of three. After these amps are<br>granted, this ability will not grant them again for<br>20 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/8c5aab1cf5fe41020ad4d994b735ba012.png\\"><\/span><span>Woodland Blessing III<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to stun and sleep by 100%.<br>When Sarisse is hit by an attack that would have<br>stunned or put her to sleep, her strength is<br>increased by 15% for 10 seconds.<br>This increase will not stack, and, after activating,<br>this buff cannot be activated again by the same<br>affliction for 15 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/58d61047bf07e78f3cf5edd26b2402392.png\\"><\/span><span>The Crimson Star<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Increases duration of buff skills by 30%.<br><br>Also, increases attack rate by 10% when the user<br>has a team strength amp and attack skill damage<br>by 20% when the user has a team defense amp.<br>Both of these effects can be applied<br>simultaneously, but neither of them will stack.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.<\/div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1643522400,"prev_article_id":"2733","next_article_id":"2794","image_path":"","update_time":1643186145}}}'